# 7. Torque Amplification Concept

Traditional bicycle:

```text
Pedal Force
      ↓
Chain
      ↓
Wheel
```

---

VELOX X-1:

```text
Pedal Force
      ↓
Pressure Storage
      ↓
Timed Release
      ↓
Chain + Stored Energy
      ↓
Wheel
```

The concept attempts to increase effective torque during periods of demand.

